      "turns": [
        {
          "speaker": "laura",
          "text": "Alright, next up is the neighborhood HOA ornament complaint. I'm Laura, chairing tonight, Will filed it, and Maya owns several of the flamingos in question."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "will",
          "text": "My complaint is simple, the front yards are becoming a themed miniature golf course."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "maya",
          "text": "That is extremely generous, thank you."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "will",
          "text": "I prepared a brief, with exhibits."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "maya",
          "text": "He brought exhibits, for gnomes."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "will",
          "text": "Forty-two pages, mostly photos."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "laura",
          "text": "We're not reading forty-two pages."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "will",
          "text": "On Maple Court alone, I counted nineteen flamingos."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "maya",
          "text": "Nine of those are mine, and they have names."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "will",
          "text": "That's the problem, Maya, they have names."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "maya",
          "text": "Phyllis is a delight."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "will",
          "text": "Phyllis is a code violation."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "laura",
          "text": "Sorry, can I just-",
          "pause_after": 0.1,
          "interrupt": true,
          "interrupt_mode": "soft_bid"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "will",
          "text": "Sure, go ahead."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "laura",
          "text": "The bylaws say tasteful, that's the whole sentence."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "maya",
          "text": "Right."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "will",
          "text": "And tasteful clearly excludes a plastic bird in a top hat."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "maya",
          "text": "Phyllis wears a sunhat, it's seasonal."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "will",
          "text": "She wore a Santa hat in July."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "maya",
          "text": "Christmas in July is a thing, Will."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "will",
          "text": "It is not a thing recognized by the bylaws, and frankly, this sets a dangerous-"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "laura",
          "text": "Will, it's a flamingo in a hat.",
          "interrupt": true,
          "interrupt_mode": "hard_cut"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "will",
          "text": "To clarify, I just mean once we allow one hat, we've opened the door to costumes."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "laura",
          "text": "Still no."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "maya",
          "text": "Can I say something, because actually-"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "will",
          "text": "If I could just-",
          "interrupt": true,
          "interrupt_mode": "failed_bid"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "laura",
          "text": "Maya has the floor, Will."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "maya",
          "text": "Thank you, last summer, three kids knocked on my door just to meet Phyllis."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "will",
          "text": "Maya, that's technically trespassing."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "maya",
          "text": "That's community.",
          "interrupt": true,
          "interrupt_mode": "reclaim"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "will",
          "text": "And we still haven't addressed the pirate ship."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "laura",
          "text": "The pirate ship is tabled until I have emotional support."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "laura",
          "text": "Can we vote please, before I age another year."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "will",
          "text": "I move to ban all decorative wildlife and humanoid figures under three feet."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "maya",
          "text": "I move to make Phyllis the official mascot."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "laura",
          "text": "I move that we adjourn and I go scream into a pillow."
        }
      ],
